            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Didius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> Eros <lb n="2"/>Didia <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Arbuscul</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Didia <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Auca <lb n="4"/>havete et tu
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bei der Auffindung noch unzerbrochen und im Kloster S. Antonius in Lezha aufbewahrt;heute ein Fragment im Muz. Hist. von Shkodra.</p>
            </div>
